data.description: This house has it ALL! Raised construction with so many amenities. This 2 bedroom and 2 bathroom (1 with handicap access)  house has an open floor plan with a beachy feel! The kitchen has an open feel with stainless appliances, vinyl/ceramicl flooring, additional trim over the windows throughout, and the layout gives a spacious feel.  Front and back decks to watch the sunset or sunrise, handicap ramp for easy access to the second floor, a new 8.25'' 8 person jacuzzi hot tub, above ground 27'' fresh water pool with deck, garage heated and cooled 300 sq foot workshop with electrical and water access, large shed for storage, under home parking for at least 6 cars, additional parking for boats or RV,  privacy fence, French drain on property, near casinos and a few blocks from Biloxi beach and so much more...this is a must see! Seller will pay up to $4,000 towards closing costs and prepaid. Schedule your showing appointment today!
